Dean Reed https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dean_Reed 0 Dean Cyril Reed (September 22, 1938 – June 13, 1986) was an American actor, singer and songwriter, director, and social activist who lived a great part of his adult life in South America and then in East Germany.
